Form990ScheduleIPartIV.Explanation: THE AROOSTOOK MEDICAL CENTER REQUESTS FUNDING OF ANY SPECIAL CAPITAL PROJECTS. SUCH FUNDING REQUESTS ARE REVIEWED BY THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS OF TAMC ENDOWMENTS AND APPROVED IF THE FUNDING IS DEEMED APPROPRIATE.

GeneralExplanation.ReturnReference: Form 990, Part VI, Line 12c: Explanation of Monitoring and Enforcement of Conflicts
GeneralExplanation.Explanation: A LIST OF ALL OFFICERS, DIRECTORS OR TRUSTEES AND KEY EMPLOYEES IS COMPILED AT THE END OF THE FISCAL YEAR. CONFLICT OF INTEREST REQUEST FORMS ARE DELIVERED TO EACH PERSON ON THE LIST. RESPONSES ARE COMPILED AND REVIEWED BY STAFF AND PRESENTED TO MANAGEMENT.

GeneralExplanation.ReturnReference: Form 990, Part VI, Line 7a: How Members or Shareholders Elect Governing Body
GeneralExplanation.Explanation: Each year at their annual meeting, the directors elect replacements for those directors whose terms are expiring. Election of directors is subject to ratification by TAMC.
